claim.claim-text:
5. An azimuth propeller device, comprising: 
a current plate member ; 
an azimuth pod fixed to the lower portion of said current plate member, said azimuth pod being provided with a propeller member, and said current plate member and said azimuth pod being provided so as to be rotatable together along a vertical axis with respect to the bottom of a ship; 
a vertical stabilizer disposed at a lower portion of said azimuth pod; and 
a trailing edge flap member rotatably attached to a rear edge portion of said vertical stabilizer.
